s, and in particular provides a least-cost routing system for cellular-to-cellular telephone calls. The first respondent is Telkom SA Limited (\'93Telkom\'94), a listed company which has a statutory monopoly in landline telephone communications in South Africa. 
 The second respondent is The Standard Bank of SA Limited (\'93Standard Bank\'94), the banking arm of a listed financial services group. The third respondent is Edgars Consolidated Stores Limited (\'93Edcon\'94), a listed retail group.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs20\lang2057\loch\f4\fs20\lang2057 
